<tr data-local-id=3D"b976c31e72d0">
<td data-local-id=3D"9005520d485e" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d9a4c4c9542e">602</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d916b76961c0" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0d6a1f50fad5">LawsonPRValidationRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6287c30b7915" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e9182ab635ad">Creates LawsonPRValidationRequest message and =
delivers to external system</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"78622169af8d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5c7058f26eb8">wfDocExportDestination</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7efbfb667cf6">
<td data-local-id=3D"658187473f5a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3f85aa6c5aad">601</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5931290cf74a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4cc06b709192">PRValidationRobotAsynchronous</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1cef96e4af63" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0d50f593357e">Creates PRValidationRequest message and delive=
rs to external system.External system responds with a PRValidationAck messa=
ge.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9aaacc286dcb" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a34be5fbc63c">wfDocExportDestination<br>
wfRobotErrorRetryCount (5) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (240)<br>
wfRobotSocketReadTimeout (30)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5baf234c2e60">
<td data-local-id=3D"946dd3968bbc" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"488d05b1bf78">603</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"066396fbf188" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"523808bb7e43">SupplierOFACCheckRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"09ab0f89f51b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ea574ad6585d">Performs OFAC check and will update DB on whet=
her there is a match or not</p>
<p local-id=3D"538a35730aba">See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://=
confluence/display/DEV/Workflow+Objects" rel=3D"nofollow">Workflow Objects<=
/a> confluence page for details on Supplier.ofacCheckPassed Workflow Object=
</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0234c1aadd93" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d979d95f7fd0">wfOFACThreshold (optional and will override th=
e default of 100).&nbsp; According to support, the typical threshold is 95<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"1b2f91c972f0"></p>
<p local-id=3D"be28425e61dd">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfOFACThreshold"&gt; &nb=
sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"d9f0bc467951">&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;95&lt;/AttrV=
alue&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"672a0759ee05">&lt;/Attribute&gt;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4ca7a5a8d0bc">
<td data-local-id=3D"c42f45a1af04" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e3495bcb53da">606</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b6f770d115eb" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"13bd1b657621">SupplierExternalVerificationRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f619bd61a347" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1377f7f3da76">Robot will perform a synchronous supplier veri=
fication to determine if the Requisition should proceed through the additio=
nal workflow steps or not. See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://co=
nfluence/display/DEV/Synchronous+External+Supplier+Check" rel=3D"nofollow">=
Synchronous Supplier Verification Robot</a> confluence page for details (14=
.2)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"44b65a98080b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"999a969973b4"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8f2eb79a6341">
<td data-local-id=3D"7a323a31a348" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d1def7d532be">609</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1ef1d9176cc7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2170784f3192">SupplierVCCheckRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4a3e532c665f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0d88285a9909">Retrieves Visual Compliance data for related s=
upplier(s) and saves the data to the DB.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"59cc3dd403dc" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c84f87b763b1"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f71829f678a9">
<td data-local-id=3D"bb439a11c892" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"41bc9c1db207">610</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fab6202475be" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"449f1ba7aa47">DelayWorkflowRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ad1bdfa62e47" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fc3ad8a77616">Adding this robot to a workflow pauses the wor=
kflow process for a configured number of minutes before it moves to next st=
ep.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"48f108c697a1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f72e7afee691">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfDelayTimerThreshold"&g=
t;<br>
&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;5&lt;/AttrValue&gt;<br>
&lt;/Attribute&gt;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2d695851512b">
<td data-local-id=3D"034de6135f2c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cfd2e2c93682">716</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"47d2c6c7867d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"105e520bb053">BudgetManagerSpendCollectionBudgetCheckPRRobot=
</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9cde8ddcc128" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ea4aec0fc5be">Budget Manager related robot. Collects spend, =
performs a budget check and flags document based on pass/fail status.</p></=
td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ce77dcd1994b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"68d1bdc652cf"></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"018eb96e6f21"></p>
