<col style=3D"width: 382.85px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4a3bb46603f9">
<th data-local-id=3D"33e0de6b06c9" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6ec3f3836dec"><strong>Id</strong></p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"75d409141f21" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"21d8e098639c"><strong>Robot Name</strong></p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"1a26749e14f4" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c89827ca2762"><strong>Description</strong></p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f8817d20e63d" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"671737c1afdf"><strong>Activity attributes (default value)</s=
trong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"378189a85ca5">
<td data-local-id=3D"1d40388c16a0" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"6d06cc202b8d" id=3D"WorkflowRobots-PORobots">PO Robots</h4>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6cf2fc459394" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"61bb9037fe92"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b33fa5710284" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"632738a81e6c"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"828065b4ae54" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"33754ef0a8f0"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"906b84b84a7b">
<td data-local-id=3D"62721b1de408" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6ac293e70e0d">5555</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bcda1b8a9b06" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c21b698511ab">PORequiresReceiptRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5987c1f92f14" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fca7410b7164">Updates the purchase order to be flagged as re=
quiring a receipt. For setup information <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D=
"http://confluence/display/CLS/Workflow+Cheat+Sheet#WorkflowCheatSheet-Requ=
iringaReceiptonaPO" rel=3D"nofollow">click this link</a>.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f6b61b65ac39" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"65dafb91fdf1"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5f4b9024da26">
<td data-local-id=3D"e4846f886259" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1b28f8d5ea6e">3333</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f5f90a529f1f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c76ab6d3c6b2">CreatePORevisionRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3ff1b2e2b784" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7223d90014f6">Creates all distribution and export documents.=
 This robot must be placed before the PODistributor robot.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a6f7d14cf572" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5f1f041f0d68"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"667f8b79475a">
<td data-local-id=3D"a89e56afb5e5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"552b4e873b5e">150</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"785aacb83436" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f7ef5879b3c6">SCTPOCreateRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0ddf6a54464b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a9094db87dbd">Creates the PO in Banner</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f45572c4c361" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1624da82edf6">wfDocExportDestination - connection name <br>
wfSCTCancelOnError - true: cancel PO on error, false: retry (false) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryCount (5) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (240)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5ff97f1443c7">
<td data-local-id=3D"9d87826e03ac" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3686f1af5b39">170</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d8227edef243" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"361130487a49">SCTPOUpdateRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3a194d9f7f88" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"565e579823cc">Receives update from Banner when the PO has be=
en "posted" in Banner. This is typically the trigger to distribute the PO t=
o the supplier.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b190ab468334" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cdbd695d6c5d">wfDocExportDestination - connection name <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryCount (5) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (240)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2e65b4ce0618">
<td data-local-id=3D"b31013c56d3e" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8ef33a331a6d">201</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d36ef1dd687d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"93ee6a5cc35a">SCTPOTaxAuthRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"336e9f565fa7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cd1ea78e46dd">Alternative Banner Budget Auth robot that acce=
pts tax information back from Banner.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"16541d43a9a1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3a63b5cab71b">wfDocExportDestination - connection name <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryCount (5) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (240)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"65460a30d8b1">
<td data-local-id=3D"b46d7ee4ed0e" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c0e32da5733a">500</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"cd17ba7d8e25" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7d3a0a0f49f7">VCardRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b4b5cb8405dd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"45121b605a2d">Requests a vcard credit card number from GE Fi=
nance (soon to be American Express). Saves the credit card number, expirati=
on date, authorization expiration date to purchase order. Should be placed =
before the CreatePORevisionRobot robot.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e9139ffe6f07" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4e7382f214d9">wfRobotErrorRetryCount (0) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (300)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ff8ff3510afe">
<td data-local-id=3D"d98232377c69" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a77d0fbec41b">501</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"55408f54580b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ed30d1a4232a">VCardPOARobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2ebf3b3575a3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b5fa67015946">Inserts the PO into the POA queue.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f1a65edc9890" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f8d19ec50b3a"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"acb3c4d473f9">
<td data-local-id=3D"9231ab9be73e" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"44aa993e8bb6">503</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a97d4e752aa0" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3fd0c5b07739">ExacTracRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5158ea6f8341" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"985dab460930">Requests a credit card number from ExacTrac. S=
aves the credit card number, expiration date, authorization expiration date=
 to purchase order. Should be placed before the CreatePORevisionRobot robot=
.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ca37bc95deaf" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d456c732faab">wfRobotErrorRetryCount (0) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (300)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"35eea5b89d11">
<td data-local-id=3D"4a16535ef80b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7a656a2c246b">550</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3d184020c7c3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eacf6aa00a24">OrgPOExportQueueEntryRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7a0ddb653b3b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3c2b53ee3310">Inserts the PO into the export queue</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4bcf38e2c795" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8e5fda691d7e">wfDocExportSchedule - schedule name (Connectio=
n Internal Name)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ea57c249543c">
<td data-local-id=3D"2839d4841b74" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ef57675c4dfe">551</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3524457c36bb" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a28883e8e599">OrgPOExportSendRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"deb83e984043" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"62ee61370eae">Performs a real-time synchronous export of the=
 PO to the external system. External system is based on the connection assi=
gned to the activity.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"05a923da6519" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ab101852e2b5">wfDocExportDestination - connection name <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryCount (0) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (300)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"be94b4d0e4b8">
<td data-local-id=3D"44d32f6b46d5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"72fc243f92bb">404</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"00fb06832475" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3952c6c3e605">ClosePORobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"72cceb550220" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2724c04adb89">Sets the AP Status of the PO to Closed.</p>
<p local-id=3D"39ae87d0e4e9"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-orange1">If r=
an a second time: WILL NOT close PO a second time</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"01641942a75c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"83084373dc24"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"491c081a3cce">
<td data-local-id=3D"c5529ca0636d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d38bba62a71d">510</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5f18a21db39c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4a34fcd7ace6">DecliningPORobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"576cd8776a4b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"89970fa2a72b">Flags a PO as only requiring cost matching. &n=
bsp;Any receipts or invoices against a flagged PO will only consider price =
when matching.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"182608bb2ede" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4aa3b574d642"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3c0e109b29cb">
<td data-local-id=3D"ae3a61861ffd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0bc8f55b3fe8">9999</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7700aec30f48" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6c3fb327a29c">CreateShipmentDemoRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"853f7d77aa82" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3b379837112a">This automated workflow robot creates sample s=
hipment documents</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"94735825fd92" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c53f87d7aff9"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"72aa5aceb478">
<td data-local-id=3D"f62fd8b6ef5b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e7331177436a">509</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a1f7015e6bff" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"16bb51f38533">OrgPONumberWheelRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2cf7be8f7a43" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"695ca6870d9e">Robot to generate PONumber from a number wheel=
. &nbsp;First looks for activiy attribute wfPONumberWheel, then if not foun=
d will look up the number wheel based on payment type. &nbsp;Used primaritl=
y for POs imported into workflow</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"589a2c1995db" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1d0dcb90a61c">wfPONumberWheel</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b686ab89538b">
<td data-local-id=3D"aac270f88227" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a65450b1dbdd">6000</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e6eb8e140d6b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a53c243341a3">PODistributionRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0eb31bd1b611" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"939bdbd46307">This robot's primary function is to create dis=
tribution entries. &nbsp;The entries are then later processed by the PODist=
ributionService.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e37b1d4ce5b8" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"37cbb0f66202"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"eebe48ab5a42">
<td data-local-id=3D"8726884f02d3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"afdd8c18fa20">6001</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3a4ee15740a3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"704fe223cc06">CreateStockOrderFromPORobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6d91eb8b5650" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"286aeece3948">Create Sales Order from PO. <strong><span clas=
s=3D"legacy-color-text-pink3">The step and PODistributor step should not be=
 configured together in one workflow process.</span></strong><span class=3D=
"legacy-color-text-pink3"> </span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0cdcf2b6ad41" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0c3b707973e6">N/A</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"470054582290">
<td data-local-id=3D"1c0264428df2" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"85644f68a9e6">603</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"684cf2e26cbd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8c25409cf655">SupplierOFACCheckRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"15efe722e206" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a38e352cbb62">Performs OFAC check and will update DB on whet=
her there is a match or not</p>
<p local-id=3D"bc00cd124f8e">See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://=
confluence/display/DEV/Workflow+Objects" rel=3D"nofollow">Workflow Objects<=
/a> confluence page for details on Supplier.ofacCheckPassed Workflow Object=
</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3acca33a550e" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5d259476b8ef">wfOFACThreshold (optional and will override th=
e default of 100).&nbsp; According to support, the typical threshold is 95<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"a75c14a93cf8"></p>
<p local-id=3D"f779ad8353c2">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfOFACThreshold"&gt; &nb=
sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"ae0fd1c0ec93">&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;95&lt;/AttrV=
alue&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"c63dd19e8bc7">&lt;/Attribute&gt;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"bc5ed92f9f7d">
<td data-local-id=3D"80a781a2a0f5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2be0be337e07">606</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e92eea092751" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a83085dd33a4">SupplierExternalVerificationRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d0d5bac03d4b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ecded046f0ce">Robot will perform a synchronous supplier veri=
fication to determine if the PO should proceed through the additional workf=
low steps or not. See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://confluence/=
display/DEV/Synchronous+External+Supplier+Check" rel=3D"nofollow">Synchrono=
us Supplier Verification Robot</a> confluence page for details(14.2)</p></t=
d>
<td data-local-id=3D"8fda633d30e3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fa42c6b8a91d"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ef62200ff907">
<td data-local-id=3D"79e7d48b5dfe" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cd476cd01009">609</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2e01a4cc87b7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8997f49b9bb9">SupplierVCCheckRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c2b398cd50bb" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d6aecb9c814f">Retrieves Visual Compliance data for related s=
upplier(s) and saves the data to the DB.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6e976e3d0acb" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8dd27007926a"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8ce616208cff">
<td data-local-id=3D"eabb6997c6e8" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6f69d22f735c">610</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2e9f7ec29bfb" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"33a87e0fb6ee">DelayWorkflowRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8988f8c908cd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b2ea20bb8de6">Adding this robot to a workflow pauses the wor=
kflow process for a configured number of minutes before it moves to next st=
ep.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f5a1bcfb75e6" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"411522e7d98d">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfDelayTimerThreshold"&g=
t;<br>
&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;5&lt;/AttrValue&gt;<br>
&lt;/Attribute&gt;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f65b62c4dcd0">
<td data-local-id=3D"a3df4e22dbe9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0056d10fb48d">558</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c7b00db1a925" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"75ff17958ad1">&nbsp;POSendEmailSubmitInvoice</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4908fe431c3a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9cda8cecdecf">Sends an email to the supplier primary remitta=
nce(email&nbsp;contact)&nbsp;requesting to open a link to submit an invoice=
</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3f9bdb7577ba" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c0033e2420b3"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8051a02c04cf">
<td data-local-id=3D"7d69077e659d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1fa0eb647509">561</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"beceedf46aad" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"03074935718e">POValidationRobotAsynchronous</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"653f72c2aaf3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"44187088de73">Sends the PurchaseOrderMessage and receives th=
e DocumentExportResponse for the first part of the asynchronous integration=
. See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://jira-jaggaer.atlassian.net/=
wiki/display/DEV/18.3+eProcurement+Internal+Release+Notes#id-18.3eProcureme=
ntInternalReleaseNotes-AsynchronousPOValidationIntegrationGreenInProgress" =
rel=3D"nofollow">ePro's 18.3 Internal Release Notes for details.</a></p></t=
d>
<td data-local-id=3D"1a7062db5874" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"356874ba6000">wfDocExportDestination<br>
wfRobotErrorRetryCount (5) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (240)<br>
wfRobotSocketReadTimeout (30)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c3805c727ad2">
<td data-local-id=3D"d6522e5eee94" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"11b479e7ece4">708</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"535cf81b0a50" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"50e0f152ace7"><span data-colorid=3D"vibk0turzy">POPDFRobot</=
span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ff25135f1e58" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2f38ed7e2e38">Creates a PDF of a PO and adds to that PO as a=
 header level, external attachment. See <a href=3D"https://jira-jaggaer.atl=
assian.net/wiki/display/DEV/19.3+eProcurement+Internal+Release+Notes#id-19.=
3eProcurementInternalReleaseNotes-NewPOPDFRobot&amp;RelatedPOValidationEnha=
ncements" rel=3D"nofollow">ePro's 19.3 Internal Release Notes</a>&nbsp;for =
details.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"21934b5c99dc" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0029264e87cf"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"78b258dce178">
<td data-local-id=3D"63e3eb12ac3a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c033fc4d14cc">709</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f6600167f867" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9f637cff9964"><span data-colorid=3D"ggq3tl0s2x">RequestJPMor=
ganVCardRobot</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d2eafef55c7a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b4f95bc0f0c8">Makes a call to JPMorgan to retrieve a credit =
card for PO as long as PO is properly configured to use JPMorgan Virtual Pa=
yments. See <a href=3D"https://jira-jaggaer.atlassian.net/wiki/display/DEV/=
19.3+ePay+Internal+Release+Notes#id-19.3ePayInternalReleaseNotes-VirtualPay=
ments" rel=3D"nofollow">ePay's 19.3 Internal Release Notes</a>&nbsp;for det=
ails.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b75389b64324" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"33b276178cde"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6cae0787db65">
<td data-local-id=3D"152030225328" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f9bc899d0787">717</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3c27455806f4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f3b7273b6fb4">BudgetManagerSpendCollectionBudgetCheckPORobot=
</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"57b63d0c5483" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"65f735853d4d">Budget Manager related robot. Collects spend, =
performs a budget check and flags document based on pass/fail status.</p></=
td>
<td data-local-id=3D"438c25c3049d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fdc785ea1024"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7a20a099560b">
<td data-local-id=3D"b0b02f0e1c48" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f986bdd52e01">724</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"29a4529fc0ae" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cf0066c0f5ec">CreateVCardPaymentRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"26f131eafed5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"34444205fb98"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-blue3">Create=
VCardPaymentRobot generates a VCard with the Conferma Pay payment processor=
</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8cd09689dcd7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"67d61e1ff744"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"894b18cfce8c">
<td data-local-id=3D"e5611a6a7136" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8c9da718bc3a">732</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2fab889ddb1e" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bfe27a05780a"><span data-colorid=3D"svdnn5hom9">ConfermaComm=
unicationRobot</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a1a0680e2197" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5ae8157bb6f4">Robot configured after both CreateVCardPayment=
Robot and PODistributionRobot in PO Workflow. Sends Card Communication thro=
ugh Conferma to Supplier. Email used is based on email distribution method<=
/p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4cc067e8b351" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2f17e98157a8"><span data-colorid=3D"ytaea3an63">wfVcardSendE=
mailPreference&nbsp;</span> - Defines a preferred email distribution type</=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"bc50354fe330">
<li local-id=3D"2a0a94a5494f">
<p local-id=3D"6efebbdcb717"><span data-colorid=3D"dyz8dj09iz">PODistMethod=
Email (Pain Text)</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a55a86e712a0">
<p local-id=3D"0ac9cb00f158"><span data-colorid=3D"pn48wsxex7">PODistMethod=
HtmlBodyEmail (HTML Body)</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"00fdbb2d1021">
<p local-id=3D"90c252b2e7df"><span data-colorid=3D"dklotvcfwt">PODistMethod=
HtmlAttachedEmail (HTML Attachment)</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5cc4dfcb5c8a">
<p local-id=3D"d97880b2ae25"><span data-colorid=3D"zehihmbnt9">PODistMethod=
PdfAttachedEmail (PDF Attachment)</span></p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
