he user inventory allocation runs under</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"874c40f6383a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"33c21127d17d">wfAutofulfillmentRobotUserName - Robot User Na=
me</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d2301e517802">
<td data-local-id=3D"16638f952ed5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"3c0988650651" id=3D"WorkflowRobots-InvoiceRobots">Invoice R=
obots</h4></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5a9d5b6f56f0" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"59281b68d615"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b0375903f8f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4bb1025ddf1b"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e33f992931ab" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b922b8480685"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"497f2c26686d">
<td data-local-id=3D"c6338280f58e" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c55de039f116">504</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"035d22379569" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"151115fa82bf">BuyerInvoiceRejectRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"726f0d3b5214" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d823a2445451">Rejects the invoice</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dcd0eb6a4f12" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"01375a55f3c4">wfActivityHelp - activity help text is saved a=
s a note in the audit trail, optional</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9166ea39fe20">
<td data-local-id=3D"e63b8da4be1a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"718270e326d0">505</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"93a2ebb82b47" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"872e477c919d">BuyerInvoiceOKToPayRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"963a1a4ef44e" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0b296b76d130">Updates the invoice's pay status to Payable (o=
r OK to Pay). This can be the trigger to queue the invoice for export.</p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ad6ac6701d7f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"55bbd6783a7b"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a105efb6340e">
<td data-local-id=3D"de83054bbe3a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"91573661b3da">506</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9ebef5a0c538" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"80bd052bc1e5">(DO NOT USE)<br>
BuyerInvoiceAutoMatchRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1fafd3d23c05" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fdc0e8704508">Performs matching on the invoice. This robot s=
upports Receipt Lead Time (time required for a receipt to be entered). To h=
old the invoice and continually match for a specified number of days, set t=
he retry count and rety interval. The retry interval is set in seconds.</p>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"439ce09060b9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4f70750bb768">wfRobotErrorRetryCount (0) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (300)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c8d87505f792">
<td data-local-id=3D"f6d86ad8c103" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6a1acfdeb704">507</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4a0c798f53fc" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"08b74d177424">CreateBuyerInvoiceRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"831e5bae7834" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"82aa572d382c">Create the Invoice from PO.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f0dabfb4785c"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-orange1">If r=
an a second time: Does create additional invoices</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a47174c1e85b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8d856b74bc82"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"de538c12a5c3">
<td data-local-id=3D"61d0a21a6dcd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c4e7ded762f6">508</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d9c647d2191a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"807cf2281e71">BuyerInvoiceClosePORobot&nbsp;</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3bec856a6fdd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3959d1f4528e">Performs setting PO A/P Status to Close when t=
he PO Match Status has reached Fully Matched status during invoice workflow=
</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"beb74259f74a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2e6d00310a50"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0ded5c702f92">
<td data-local-id=3D"bc7b1a5a9b77" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2f3d0406cf56">511</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"64d3ee00ee3a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a08763c7a952">BuyerInvoiceHoldUntilMatchedRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f47d0e9d02e4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"89d94f8c4da5">Similar to auto match, this robot holds invoic=
es until they are matched or come within one of two date attributes (duedat=
e or discountdate)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"20fd59a48388" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9f02ec8a4acd">wfRobotErrorRetryCount (optional)</p>
<p local-id=3D"fda6a8ffdcc7">wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (optional) wfEarlyRe=
lease_DaysBeforeDueDate wfEarlyRelease_DaysBeforeDiscountDate</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"24ecdcd4daad">
<td data-local-id=3D"8d159e5aeae9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"810695a7f39a">512</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c19f2049d1a2" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a956b7b0de82">SubmitOCRInvoiceRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b899f46b0603" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9c50deb75e02">This Robot submits the imported invoice throug=
h any of the imported files.</p>
<p local-id=3D"62ebdfcf3ff6">This Robot&nbsp;<span class=3D"legacy-color-te=
xt-blue3">flips invoices in "Not Ready for Matching" status to "Unmatched" =
and triggers the initial matching, just like when manual invoices are submi=
tted.</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fb3cbfe6ca1a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0a5f7293e967"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-blue3">The wo=
rkflow robot is setup as follows:</span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">&lt;Fol=
der name=3D"Ready for Matching"&nbsp;folderType=3D"automated"&gt;
&lt;WorkflowType&gt;invoice&lt;/WorkflowType&gt;
&lt;FolderRobot&gt;SubmitOCRInvoiceRobot&lt;/FolderRobot&gt;
&lt;/Folder&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"dfbb5b5eec49">The activity configuration looks like this:</p=
>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">&lt;Act=
ivity name=3D"Ready for Matching"&gt;
&lt;ActivityType&gt;automated&lt;/ActivityType&gt;
&lt;StepRef name=3D"Ready for Matching" /&gt;
&lt;FolderRef name=3D"Ready for Matching" /&gt;
&lt;Rule&gt;&lt;![CDATA [  Document.Source =3D=3D "Invoice_Import"  ]]&gt;&=
lt;/Rule&gt;
&lt;FolderSelectionRule&gt;ExplicitFolder&lt;/FolderSelectionRule&gt;
&lt;Flag&gt;HideMatchActionOnApproveComplete&lt;/Flag&gt;
&lt;/Activity&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d5c10689444c">
<td data-local-id=3D"fa25debb42d5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"baa0b5cd8a01">513</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4425f3528522" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"389b52b4a3f9">BuyerInvoiceNumberWheelRobot</p></td>
