<p local-id=3D"092359f23a8e"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5be36c668fad">
<td data-local-id=3D"de47ae74d500" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6f3b82306fd3">123</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e7736fbfd453" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cc744ff857d1">SCTInvoiceBudgetAuthRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"64246a07453a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d12544c67190">Budget Authorization check against banner.</p>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e8ffca8de7b2" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ab75b293b0da"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"55f384924a43">
<td data-local-id=3D"0c0459b58a38" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b5d3443bafdf">603</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6eabd32b49d7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f9e2a6e74be4">SupplierOFACCheckRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d93f2533e876" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"acecf706fc9d">Performs OFAC check and will update DB on whet=
her there is a match or not</p>
<p local-id=3D"35ac4d8d83b7">See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://=
confluence/display/DEV/Workflow+Objects" rel=3D"nofollow">Workflow Objects<=
/a> confluence page for details on Supplier.ofacCheckPassed Workflow Object=
</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"43a9062fc7d7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8348c3e030ef">wfOFACThreshold (optional and will override th=
e default of 100).&nbsp; According to support, the typical threshold is 95<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"3a0b88154fcd"></p>
<p local-id=3D"c074edae831c">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfOFACThreshold"&gt; &nb=
sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"e8b98e27a666">&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;95&lt;/AttrV=
alue&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"2a0e71357326">&lt;/Attribute&gt;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4cc364125c1d">
<td data-local-id=3D"bf486ea2891d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8001daa84e64">606</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5526dc895cc3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f4aeaa55006e">SupplierExternalVerificationRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f7c1e7e726c1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"22a2777173b9">Robot will perform a synchronous supplier veri=
fication to determine if the Invoice should proceed through the additional =
workflow steps or not. See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://conflu=
ence/display/DEV/Synchronous+External+Supplier+Check" rel=3D"nofollow">Sync=
hronous Supplier Verification Robot</a> confluence page for details(14.2)</=
p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"74a4557d949c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b25d4547fe5d"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d408e13b28ff">
<td data-local-id=3D"1a3b9aa401c8" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"12bc793f92ea">610</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"22e2e0483cb2" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"67e167500f90">DelayWorkflowRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e4314b7f5668" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1e23ce0988e4">Adding this robot to a workflow pauses the wor=
kflow process for a configured number of minutes before it moves to next st=
ep.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"362c351d4956" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"88714376ad86">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfDelayTimerThreshold"&g=
t;<br>
&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;5&lt;/AttrValue&gt;<br>
&lt;/Attribute&gt;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"fc5828bb42b9">
<td data-local-id=3D"0c3d882d3509" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f06f2fcd7769">514</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"93eacaaeb7c2" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"67eeea82888e"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-default">GetT=
axEngineValueRobot</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f921f0520957" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"69fe9d52bd18">Performs a tax engine callout to a third party=
 tax engine provider if tax engine integration is enabled. The&nbsp;robot d=
oes not attempt to make a callout if tax engine integration is&nbsp;disable=
d.&nbsp;</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"037042da7909" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"80dce3c2e6ac"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"45b5a6c61594">
<td data-local-id=3D"675ada45cf40" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a7e23e6497e8">552</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"98b554cfccf4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3dc2a7f79edf"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-default">Buye=
rInvoiceForceClosePORobot</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4348ea252cff" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"35f9e6a4bebe">Performs a force close on the&nbsp;PO even if =
it is not fully matched. The PO A/P status is modified when this is used.</=
p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"82eae9550ed0" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fc77512cb828"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"436071b2b4df">
<td data-local-id=3D"2f1e398d5e51" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"87b792bfe3c2">700</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e2c55fc1717b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bae7a31d4d4b">BuyerInvoiceValidationRobotAsynchronous</p></t=
d>
<td data-local-id=3D"ce9d83a44990" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a42dd2ae5417">Performs an auto check to a generic (non banne=
r specific) ERP to verify if there is enough money in the budget</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3d4bb7a85e68" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cc093b638a39">This robot supports flags and attributes on th=
e related activity in the worfklow process definition:</p>
<div id=3D"expander-147804969" class=3D"expand-container">
<div id=3D"expander-control-147804969" class=3D"expand-control">
<span class=3D"expand-control-icon"><img style=3D"vertical-align:middle;" c=
lass=3D"expand-control-image" src=3D"d7d53092439c58d5c8a0526ed3502cd054299a=
c119b32fd80139d5972d26584e" width=3D"16" height=3D"16"></span><span class=
=3D"expand-control-text">Click here for an example activity in XML format</=
span>
</div>
<div id=3D"expander-content-147804969" class=3D"expand-content">
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">    &lt=
;Activity name=3D"Invoice Budget"&gt;
    &lt;ActivityType&gt;automated&lt;/ActivityType&gt;
    &lt;StepRef name=3D"Invoice Budget" /&gt;
    &lt;FolderRef name=3D"Invoice Budget" /&gt;
    &lt;Rule&gt;&lt;![CDATA[true]]&gt;&lt;/Rule&gt;
    &lt;FolderSelectionRule&gt;ExplicitFolder&lt;/FolderSelectionRule&gt;
=09&lt;Flag&gt;NoBypass&lt;/Flag&gt;
    &lt;Flag&gt;BuyerInvoiceValidationRobotStep&lt;/Flag&gt;
    &lt;Attribute name=3D"wfDocExportDestination"&gt;
      &lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;InvoiceBudgetCheck&lt;/AttrValue&gt=
;
    &lt;/Attribute&gt;
    &lt;Attribute name=3D"wfRobotErrorRetryCount"&gt;
      &lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;1&lt;/AttrValue&gt;
    &lt;/Attribute&gt;
    &lt;Attribute name=3D"wfRobotErrorRetryInterval"&gt;
      &lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;30&lt;/AttrValue&gt;
    &lt;/Attribute&gt;
    &lt;Attribute name=3D"wfRobotSocketReadTimeout"&gt;
      &lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;180&lt;/AttrValue&gt;
    &lt;/Attribute&gt;
    &lt;Attribute name=3D"wfActivityHelp"&gt;
      &lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;The invoice is sent to the ERP to v=
alidate budget information.&lt;/AttrValue&gt;
    &lt;/Attribute&gt;
  &lt;/Activity&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8b01860bfd10">
<td data-local-id=3D"ac98c1c3841d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"db5f14294301">701</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a57490c8804c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ca23d9bd449e">BuyerInvoiceSignatureValidationRobot</p>
<p local-id=3D"a105a1db5271">DO NOT USE - this has been deprecated</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"96bc6f4d7f98" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6ca3f7f6ed0b">Send signed cXML invoice to TrustWeaver for va=
lidation.</p>
<p local-id=3D"61c4712e2a0b">Defaults hardcoded for TrustWeaver Intgration =
are:</p>
<p local-id=3D"f251726da4c2">Max Retry Count after error: 4</p>
<p local-id=3D"10bd3e351429">Max time they will accept retry attempts after=
 the initial attempt: 10 hours</p>
<p local-id=3D"c91d78912314">JAGGAER will retry every 2.5 hours to evenly b=
reak up the 10 hour max time limit.</p>
<p local-id=3D"36aaeeea0de8">17.1 Added functionality to robot to wait for =
Async response when validating Trustweaver Chile, Job will complete the rob=
ot step when the response is posted by Trustweaver as OK.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"37c419d1d8de" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e68526556297">The concepts of retry count, retry interval an=
d connection timeout will be hard coded to match the expectations of TrustW=
eaver. They will not be something you can override with attributes.</p></td=
>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ecb15dc10c5e">
<td data-local-id=3D"41550aaf47b7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e8f1c3977030">702</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"64403ab84b0f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"179579d8de6b"><span data-colorid=3D"o6syazbzph">BuyerInvoice=
SigningRobot</span></p>
<p local-id=3D"db33f59a8ba8"><span data-colorid=3D"thyruksrx8">DO NOT USE -=
 this has been deprecated</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"16cbdcf371ea" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e56aefc548a8">For electronic invoice buyer signature for Tru=
stWeaver Chile</p>
<p local-id=3D"459ee4966148">Performs a call out to TrustWeaver to get elec=
tronic signature (Certificate Stamp) for the Chilean electronic invoice. St=
ep is configured for 3 occurrences during workflow as 3 signatures (Certifi=
cate Stamp) are required for the invoice.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d713dafb9c68" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"688c1344e757"><span data-colorid=3D"nig44epqxs">wfAcknowledg=
eReception - Typically an automated step after the invoice is received by t=
he buyer to get the first signature</span></p>
<p local-id=3D"f615cdfe969f"><span data-colorid=3D"a8yv4eaq2b">wfCommercial=
AcceptanceRejection - Manual step before this robot for buyer to confirm th=
at they accept the invoice</span></p>
<p local-id=3D"9c963c3b629b"><span data-colorid=3D"bz4fhd4979">wfAcknowledg=
eGoodsServiceDelivery - Manual step before this robot for the buyer to conf=
irm they have accepted the delivery of goods or services</span></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"83b752ce560e">
<td data-local-id=3D"266a7d50a36c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dd8e69d05c8d">562</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8a091b4f5b88" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"74617622e2cc"><span data-colorid=3D"ts8702wch0">BuyerInvoice=
DocumentSigningRobot</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"34946165b3ed" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"68ee72caf4a9"><span data-colorid=3D"zqj3lyk5yc">The workflow=
 robot for signing will initiate a post to the endpoint, receive an acknowl=
edgement, and place the invoice on hold.&nbsp;Error handling is also includ=
ed.&nbsp;Issuance Status is populated as "Pending" if the post was successf=
ul or "Error" if it had an error.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"81896d29590c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"207901bc93a2"><span data-colorid=3D"wbpyne5e2y">&lt;Flag&gt;=
InvoiceSignatureActivity&lt;/Flag&gt;</span></p>
<p local-id=3D"6dff64bb6dc2"><span data-colorid=3D"kaml05xfiy">wfCompliance=
RobotMaxWaitTimeMinutes - Overrides the default time period where the robot=
 could enten in error status.</span></p>
<p local-id=3D"345af3e12ebf"><span data-colorid=3D"xhjoqygmnr">If empty - t=
akes default time =3D 10 minutes&nbsp;</span><br><span data-colorid=3D"mp0c=
3fv9z0">Min value =3D 10 minutes</span><br><span data-colorid=3D"i51h8bwpft=
">Max value =3D 10080 minutes (7days)</span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">&lt;Att=
ribute name=3D"wfComplianceRobotMaxWaitTimeMinutes"&gt;
=09&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;10&lt;/AttrValue&gt;
&lt;/Attribute&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"34736c21ce6e">
<td data-local-id=3D"32965605cd3d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"92346c24851c">563</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6b8367c94279" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"813e367333ab"><span data-colorid=3D"o21xlvavnl">BuyerInvoice=
DocumentArchivingRobot</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e633ec7f530a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cdd42044273f"><span data-colorid=3D"dyzljl3vjh">The workflow=
 robot for archiving will initiate a post to the endpoint, receive an ackno=
wledgement, and place the invoice on hold.&nbsp;Archive Status is populated=
 as "Pending" if the post was successful or "Error" if it had an error.&nbs=
p;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5e60785c63cf" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ff5897b8b1c3"><span data-colorid=3D"f5b2402mna">&lt;Flag&gt;=
InvoiceArchiveActivity&lt;/Flag&gt;</span></p>
<p local-id=3D"834a17bf8765"><span data-colorid=3D"f9m1f7djd9">wfCompliance=
RobotMaxWaitTimeMinutes - Overrides the default time period where the robot=
 could enten in error status.</span></p>
<p local-id=3D"fbcbd2096e47"><span data-colorid=3D"uoggrrvlxo">If empty - t=
akes default time =3D 10 minutes&nbsp;</span><br><span data-colorid=3D"tqaw=
loc90p">Min value =3D 10 minutes</span><br><span data-colorid=3D"rfrzdw6875=
">Max value =3D 10080 minutes (7days)</span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">&lt;Att=
ribute name=3D"wfComplianceRobotMaxWaitTimeMinutes"&gt;
=09&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;10&lt;/AttrValue&gt;
&lt;/Attribute&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div></td>
</tr>
