<tr data-local-id=3D"969a998084c6">
<td data-local-id=3D"1342e55a6c6d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"67ffc6216740">555</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2f4e949861ce" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b41db2c43fc9">ReturnInvoiceRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6b6e7b32cf8d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e3a0ed53bf5e"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-default">Non-=
PO Invoice Robot that auto-returns the invoice when the invoice contains no=
n-po lines. If the invoice enters the system from the Supplier Portal or DM=
R, the import will throw a workflow error.</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3e3ebe19ae20" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6da725387508">Documented at: <a href=3D"https://jira-jaggaer=
.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/DEV/pages/74827592/15.3+Banyan+Internal+Release+=
Notes+HotList#id-15.3BanyanInternalReleaseNotes(HotList)-15.3BanyanInternal=
ReleaseNotes(HotList)-Auto-ReturnInvoicesinworkflowwithNO-POlines-----MR" d=
ata-linked-resource-id=3D"74827592" data-linked-resource-version=3D"89" dat=
a-linked-resource-type=3D"page">15.3 Banyan Internal Release Notes (HotList=
)#15.3BanyanInternalReleaseNotes(HotList)-Auto-ReturnInvoicesinworkflowwith=
NO-POlines-----MR</a></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e59699ef0c6b">
<td data-local-id=3D"ddcbc193ed54" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"111bf1249368" id=3D"WorkflowRobots-PaymentRobots">Payment R=
obots</h4></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"72c4e5e2084c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"506c5b06ffc8"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0d95344292c9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4f016fedaf49"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"add2ed5c23ae" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bfc7d6843aca"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4791bf6f48bd">
<td data-local-id=3D"e23f7a84cb4c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0f0398d8fab8">722</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0a536de6d693" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a285b88fef56"><span data-colorid=3D"sxz7l7dukn">PaymentAddCr=
editMemoRobot</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6f030ab43f1d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c1db4f0abaf0">This Robot&nbsp;<span class=3D"legacy-color-te=
xt-blue3">supports the integration of Credit Memos into a Payment doc; so t=
hat a Credit Memo can be used as a payment offset within a payment being ge=
nerated.</span>&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"334fd2d45b32"></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4d94bb048c2b">
<li local-id=3D"bd16af320843">
<p local-id=3D"d734379f08e3">Use SQL search for "Payable" Credit Memos</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"eef7f92699dd">
<p local-id=3D"c145742e7916">Existing Filter Strategy:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fb1e04d3c191">
<li local-id=3D"f15b0bd66e7d">
<p local-id=3D"0a8b79db9ffb">Credit Memos&nbsp;</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c9e53daecf5f">
<p local-id=3D"b63e5aa061a2">Same client (Org)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"81f0a4970f84">
<p local-id=3D"7d8b8a786bff">Same Currency</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c428fbfcbe0">
<p local-id=3D"743dbd6654bc">Credit Memo must be Payable (Pay Status)</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"19300c5989c5">
<p local-id=3D"8253322b9af1">Credit Memo must not be assigned to a Jaggaer =
Pay Payment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"64689ba73222">
<p local-id=3D"bfa946670216">Same Supplier</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e262dff08a4c">
<p local-id=3D"eb3fb4b4c891">Same Remit To Address</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"040af663c37f">
<p local-id=3D"4c6857c6190e">Will fetch first 10 results</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"8dcfd3e97e8c">
<p local-id=3D"720c07464c07">Robot adds as many of the Credit Memos as poss=
ible.&nbsp;</p>
<ul local-id=3D"26dc8b3b483d">
<li local-id=3D"ffd662d8083f">
<p local-id=3D"664e2dfd8679">As each credit memo is added, payment amount i=
s adjusted to make sure that total payment amount never goes below 0$</p></=
li>
</ul></li>
</ul></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c5f282c657d7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c42f61b26ca2"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-blue3">The wo=
rkflow robot is setup as follows:</span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">&lt;Wor=
kflowFolderMessage&gt;=20
&nbsp;  &lt;Folder name=3D"Add Credit Memo" folderType=3D"automated"&gt;
   =09&lt;WorkflowType&gt;payment&lt;/WorkflowType&gt;
    &lt;FolderRobot&gt;PaymentAddCreditMemoRobot&lt;/FolderRobot&gt;
   &lt;/Folder&gt;
&lt;/WorkflowFolderMessage&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"f760fb546984">The activity configuration looks like this:</p=
>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">&lt;Act=
ivity name=3D"Add Credit Memo"&gt;
    &lt;ActivityType&gt;automated&lt;/ActivityType&gt;
    &lt;StepRef name=3D"Add Credit Memo" /&gt;
    &lt;FolderRef name=3D"Add Credit Memo" /&gt;
    &lt;Rule&gt;&lt;![CDATA[true]]&gt;&lt;/Rule&gt;
    &lt;FolderSelectionRule&gt;ExplicitFolder&lt;/FolderSelectionRule&gt;  =
&lt;/Activity&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a65f6628e4f9">
<td data-local-id=3D"45a9701b30ab" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"41acd1f50fd3">725</p></td>
