<tr data-local-id=3D"265336b4da76">
<td data-local-id=3D"204578803cd8" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cdf44b4a6b8d">603</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8514a255d0d4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f3e1651fa2a5">SupplierOFACCheckRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f48acff54624" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d8d25998e686">Performs OFAC check and will update DB on whet=
her there is a match or not</p>
<p local-id=3D"0683b2581ee3">See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://=
confluence/display/DEV/Workflow+Objects" rel=3D"nofollow">Workflow Objects<=
/a> confluence page for details on Supplier.ofacCheckPassed Workflow Object=
</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c5b26437261b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"827510979d18">wfOFACThreshold (optional and will override th=
e default of 100).&nbsp; According to support, the typical threshold is 95<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"214b138df81d">&lt;Folder name=3D"OFAC Supplier Check" folder=
Type=3D"automated"&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;WorkflowType&gt;supplierregis=
tration&lt;/WorkflowType&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;FolderRobot&gt;Supplier=
OFACCheckRobot&lt;/FolderRobot&gt; &nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"a5f28d6bbe72">&lt;/Folder&gt;</p>
<p local-id=3D"03ccb1a44dfa"></p>
<p local-id=3D"fc51c94d092b">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfOFACThreshold"&gt; &nb=
sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"e2df1c60aacf">&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;95&lt;/AttrV=
alue&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"5688fed4c134">&lt;/Attribute&gt;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c3294702b22f">
<td data-local-id=3D"30f86d347d59" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a3a09ee64e73">604</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8a5159657923" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a1ad643cd3fb">SupplierERPExportRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ffee880cf6ed" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"92f51f7e5231">When a Supplier Registration passes through th=
is automated wf step, it will set the ApprovedForERPSync flag true and add =
the supplier to the TSMRealTimeSupplierExportQueue to be exported to the ER=
P</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fa53d6756401" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3b6c2e0d1ee0">&nbsp;&lt;Folder name=3D"Sync to ERP" folderTy=
pe=3D"automated"&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;WorkflowType&gt;supplierregistr=
ation&lt;/WorkflowType&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;FolderRobot&gt;SupplierER=
PExportRobot&lt;/FolderRobot&gt; &nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"7bedfb746130">&lt;/Folder&gt;</p>
<p local-id=3D"33a6154a5208"></p>
<p local-id=3D"890224eb74c2">&lt;Activity name=3D"Sync to ERP"&gt; &nbsp;&n=
bsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"9f60bfd4590e">&lt;ActivityType&gt;automated&lt;/ActivityType=
&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"967b1081ec01">&lt;StepRef name=3D"Sync to ERP" /&gt; &nbsp;&=
nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"6427b698d1ae">&lt;FolderRef name=3D"Sync to ERP" /&gt; &nbsp=
;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"77a67965bb1a">&lt;Rule&gt;&lt;![CDATA[Document.isRegistratio=
nShortForm =3D=3D false]]&gt;&lt;/Rule&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;FolderSel=
ectionRule&gt;ExplicitFolder&lt;/FolderSelectionRule&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=
</p>
<p local-id=3D"b546c8c515e5">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfActivityHelp"&gt; &nbs=
p;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"f5a6925d95c8">&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;Flags the su=
pplier for ERP integration&lt;/AttrValue&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"7cbeb88a4668">&lt;/Attribute&gt; &nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"d7a5af1b74d9">&lt;/Activity&gt;</p>
<p local-id=3D"b1a4a1d52eae"></p>
<p local-id=3D"943104151d5d"></p>
<p local-id=3D"5129bc116a37"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"45102852d97d">
<td data-local-id=3D"7eeee2162b54" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c666bed240fb">605&nbsp;</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"39fc7c2f290c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"49452e9349f0">ExternalSupplierCheckRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a7e470bc4a59" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"83ac9ed3bd08">Supplier Registration workflow&nbsp;will perfo=
rm an external supplier check so that the customer can determine if the sup=
plier should proceed through the additional workflow steps or not.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6792f75c7fd1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a88f20a3a822"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"67397b8bfb7d">
<td data-local-id=3D"6ef18e475ebd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"045323a732b3">606</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a1a82dadf85f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"76be23506ebc">SupplierExternalVerificationRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5594db2a6609" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f28cb6b5aef4">Robot will perform a synchronous supplier veri=
fication to determine if the Registration should proceed through the additi=
onal workflow steps or not. See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://c=
onfluence/display/DEV/Synchronous+External+Supplier+Check" rel=3D"nofollow"=
>Synchronous Supplier Verification Robot</a> confluence page for details(14=
.2)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"403e62587f37" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b7e759d1d410"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5f89a27b7e32">
<td data-local-id=3D"2aadb8c43b24" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"70e65f76df0a"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9792226e4e70" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5460ec77aab0">&nbsp;SupplierDuplicateCheckRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9a0be42b36d9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ac17c476bb4e">&nbsp;Robot will perform duplicate checking du=
ring supplier registration workflow for a notification based on the attribu=
tes that are chosen in the attribute column.&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"f6c70e3cd717"></p>
<p local-id=3D"67dc628bbb1b">If this step is triggered, a notification will=
 appear for users subscribed to the "Suppier Request Potential Duplicate Su=
pplier" Notification</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d4d227e2bd61" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2c7512e992c6">&lt;Folder name=3D"Duplicate Robot Folder" fol=
derType=3D"automated"&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;WorkflowType&gt;supplierre=
gistration&lt;/WorkflowType&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;FolderRobot&gt;Suppl=
ierDuplicateCheckRobot&lt;/FolderRobot&gt; &nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"f3c390bbb59e">&lt;/Folder&gt;</p>
<p local-id=3D"1ee277693d57"></p>
<p local-id=3D"ea4072f1d0a3">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfCheckSupplierName"&gt;=
 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"7b379be1b960">&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;true&lt;/Att=
rValue&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"3c6c212401f8">&lt;/Attribute&gt;</p>
<p local-id=3D"59ed0280b0b1"></p>
<p local-id=3D"fb763dca24ae">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfCheckSupplierTIN"&gt; =
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"0726c01c30ec">&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;true&lt;/Att=
rValue&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"0b31328d684b">&lt;/Attribute&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"5c4240abcfec"></p>
<p local-id=3D"0bf49dca55ed">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfCheckSupplierDUNS"&gt;=
 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"9db65d40a17a">&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;true&lt;/Att=
rValue&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"21791250a42b">&lt;/Attribute&gt;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"917923085f69">
