her there is a match or not</p>
<p local-id=3D"9b7c97f9a67e">See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://=
confluence/display/DEV/Workflow+Objects" rel=3D"nofollow">Workflow Objects<=
/a> confluence page for details on Supplier.ofacCheckPassed Workflow Object=
</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bee85505030b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eab4d4cb75a3">wfOFACThreshold (optional and will override th=
e default of 100).&nbsp; According to support, the typical threshold is 95<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"acb05cf7ee6a"></p>
<p local-id=3D"e0c0ba961963">&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfOFACThreshold"&gt; &nb=
sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"5df9f863c787">&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;95&lt;/AttrV=
alue&gt; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"e12141da83da">&lt;/Attribute&gt;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6803b2b7fbe7">
<td data-local-id=3D"046195b9caef" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b03c07f6bd7">604</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7e74cd39b2d9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5ce465cead28">SupplierERPExportRobot</p></td>
