fication to determine if Supplier Managment should proceed through the addi=
tional workflow steps or not. See <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http:/=
/confluence/display/DEV/Synchronous+External+Supplier+Check" rel=3D"nofollo=
w">Synchronous Supplier Verification Robot</a> confluence page for details(=
