<p local-id=3D"a51f6eb48cfe">SupplierVCCheckRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"88728746071a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"de736ad8b5a1">Retrieves Visual Compliance data for related s=
upplier(s) and saves the data to the DB.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7dba81c22f19" class=3D"confluenceTd">
