<p local-id=3D"3d53c09c7189">720</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7e5d4c4af852" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"98786b0aadd0"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-blue3">Suppli=
erTINValidationRobot</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"84682816feb3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b66ae584bb96">22.2 TIN Validation Robot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d9b13e082f24" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"077eb623f7a3"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"77a336cb8aff">
<td data-local-id=3D"dd70e310c0a6" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8f7d91a83e61">728</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e7622deeb9fa" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e4fd9a1eff23"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-blue3">Paymen=
tSupplierProvisioningRobot</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ca9ef06f15be" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c1ccb26bb3da"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-blue3">New Ro=
bot to auto-provision the supplier for JAGGAER Pay administration, when the=
y go through the standard TSM registration process.</span></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"06d26719171b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f3d5bae2f519"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-blue3">New Su=
pplier provisioning Workflow Robot XML</span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">&lt;Fol=
der name=3D"Supplier Provisioning" folderType=3D"automated"&gt;
&lt;WorkflowType&gt;suppliermanagement&lt;/WorkflowType&gt;
&lt;FolderRobot&gt;PaymentSupplierProvisioningRobot&lt;/FolderRobot&gt;
&lt;/Folder&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"55a3e6510d79"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-blue3">Proces=
s Config Robot Step XML:</span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">&lt;Act=
ivity name=3D"Payment Supplier Provisioning"&gt;
&lt;ActivityType&gt;automated&lt;/ActivityType&gt;
&lt;StepRef name=3D"Payment Supplier Provisioning" /&gt;
&lt;FolderRef name=3D"Supplier Provisioning" /&gt;
&lt;Rule&gt;&lt;![CDATA[true]]&gt;&lt;/Rule&gt;
&lt;FolderSelectionRule&gt;ExplicitFolder&lt;/FolderSelectionRule&gt;
&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfActivityHelp"&gt;
&lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;Supplier provisioning for active payment =
accounts&lt;/AttrValue&gt;
&lt;/Attribute&gt;
&lt;/Activity&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0299e9b10de9">
<td data-local-id=3D"e545e06e8831" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0edb61fa564d">735</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d934cdd5c435" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f0ea1eddb600">SupplierTrustpairValidationRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b362b30ce284" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5732fad26a71">Triggers a request to Trustpair for any suppli=
er bank accounts that do not yet have a Trustpair status. The step that thi=
s robot operates in will hold until all bank accounts have recieved a statu=
s from Trustpair. If the supplier enters the robot step and already has sat=
uts values for of the bank accounts, there is no action and proceeds to the=
 next step.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3eb69b37c2b7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"28dec117fb7e"></p></td>
</tr>
