<td data-local-id=3D"731caca1e565" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9733186f3836">SupplierExternalVerificationRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f89d7b2d0260" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c1beba6981c5">Sourcing event workflow&nbsp;will perform a sy=
nchronous supplier verification to determine if the sourcing event should p=
roceed through the additional workflow steps or not. See <a class=3D"extern=
al-link" href=3D"http://confluence/display/DEV/Synchronous+External+Supplie=
r+Check" rel=3D"nofollow">Synchronous Supplier Verification Robot</a> confl=
uence page for details(14.2)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f3cbd959eb56" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d72fe0ba591b"></p></td>
