<tr data-local-id=3D"8492fe3a9238">
<td data-local-id=3D"6c44ccdc76c7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"e28aa6f70215" id=3D"WorkflowRobots-SourcingEventEvaluationR=
obots">Sourcing Event&nbsp;Evaluation&nbsp;Robots</h4></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4ab03bd1dc43" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"134909159679"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6745a3cfc059" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"857217c96e37"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d5e2ea00bb90" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"22d079e47dcd"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"158fadd24f23">
<td data-local-id=3D"b4222fbcb05f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"35c354955a3e">607&nbsp;</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"222fe744cdc4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dd04ad388985">&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"114a8399d80e">SourcingEventAwardToSupplierRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ac63316b43aa" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fa516dd0ae60">&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"3201bc9767a5">Used only&nbsp;in Sourcing Event Evaluation wo=
rkflow, the&nbsp;robot will take the response marked as awarded and will au=
tomatically award the event to that response. The robot is required for Eva=
luation workflow and&nbsp;should do the following to the event:Change the s=
tatus to awarded and Mark the selected response as awarded.&nbsp; If there =
is no supplier awarded there is a failed audit entry and it goes into an er=
ror state.&nbsp; If the event does not flow through the robot the event sta=
tus is changed to&nbsp;Close Without Awarding. As of the 15.1 release, this=
 robot also initiates a summarization process for each supplier on the even=
t. It adds rows to the sourcingdirector.eventsupplierbidsummary table. That=
 table is used for creating Sourcing Reports. If the event fails during sum=
marization, then this workflow process will not complete and the step will =
be put into an error state.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8616964b3e5c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e288d5eb37b5"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"031adf0791bd">
<td data-local-id=3D"bf7a68464f2f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9ec0eb2a77f3">609</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d1e2b09319be" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"28260b9ef28c">SupplierVCCheckRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b7a79df26a86" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b8bb1ff6c09f">Retrieves Visual Compliance data for related s=
upplier(s) and saves the data to the DB.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"594d50ea17db" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f40cf230d83a"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"35b3c3b61c80">
<td data-local-id=3D"7dcacaf2bef9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"25d0b9efd930" id=3D"WorkflowRobots-ContractRobots">Contract=
&nbsp;Robots</h4></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5f1038895666" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"542d009a160a"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d39286bd5d36" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"372ae1e2c592"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b8a590872204" class=3D"confluenceTd">
