</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7a6554361532">
<td data-local-id=3D"d79c0cab5880" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"06fdf319fefb">553</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"45b23f5a1ac8" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7eedeae9bc1f">ContractSendToEsignServiceRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"547bec8e9fc0" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"03ef7007e10c">Used in contract workflow to send the contract=
 to the ESignature service. If the contract is not using esign, it will pro=
gress to the next steps in the workflow (out for signature). It has a valid=
ation for Jurisdiction that doesn't allow eSignature,&nbsp; it will get an =
error while trying to send to eSignature Service, to fix it, it will requir=
e a Jurisdiction that allows eSignature.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"77fe9094ebac" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ff95129965d6"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5dd6de095667">
<td data-local-id=3D"6238780e630b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8d2bb4b4661a">556</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"26d3e53756d2" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"adf19d5d4935">CMRContractERPExportRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"142f68e11a18" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b731eb10425d">Used in contract workflow to send the contract=
 to the Contract Export Queue which sends XML to external system based on t=
he connection and schedule in Document Export framework</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b9b9436a8cce" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e6fbb18678d7"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"327490dbc87e">
<td data-local-id=3D"67693536a798" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2245d864e5ba">557</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ed377c8b9892" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"02d3981d063d">ExternalContractValidationRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1b096f032fe7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c42e9d8ae138">Asynchronous robot used in contract workflow t=
o send message to external system (step 1) and receive a response with stat=
us and update custom contract fields (step 2). The status will prompt an ap=
prove or return action in workflow. The custom fields will be updated on th=
e contract in SelectSite/TCM.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"129d62e7a370" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2b39be4b8fd3"></p></td>
</tr>
