<tr data-local-id=3D"5b5dbdd3dd94">
<td data-local-id=3D"5d125f29e84c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"584fc62c98bf" id=3D"WorkflowRobots-Intake(Orchestration)For=
mRequestRobots">Intake (Orchestration) Form Request Robots</h4></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0b06ce38946a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5dee9952fcee"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d4979a63d2b7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2441c356e8a1"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d04e87bea03c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"72454bef7285"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e7e87d7f6708">
<td data-local-id=3D"1be42a32b16f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4b1916a753ed">729</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dd6875a96cf4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"25a3eae69576">CreateRequisitionRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0cb931dbd6d4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"086ccb6fda8b">Used in Intake / Orchestration Requests to cre=
ate a new Requisition using the Intake Form Request and submits that new PR=
 to its own PR workflow.&nbsp; The robot will then wait till the PR complet=
es workflow before moving on.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7c68356bb7b5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fc9d8a7fa20d"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8a08075c31e9">
<td data-local-id=3D"9cc61f9f2c19" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ca0e6864bc4a">730</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a6358f46461f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8f093119e939">CreateOrchestrationPORobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"318c04050a66" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"af4468ca4614">Used in Intake / Orchestration Requests to cre=
ate a new Purchase Order using the PR that was created from the same Intake=
 Form Request and submits that new PO to its own PO workflow.&nbsp; The rob=
ot will then wait till the PO completes workflow before moving on.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"55f90f0b1e71" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7ae176d4a973"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d6aeed946af4">
<td data-local-id=3D"383833b4e167" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1249ed3386bb"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-blue3">731</s=
pan></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d626c50bef80" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"437ce50f031a">CreateContractFromOrchestrationRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e4f285f06547" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"87acaf6fa8c7">Used in Intake / Orchestration Requests to cre=
ate a new Contract using the Intake Form Request and submits that new Contr=
act to its own Contract workflow.&nbsp; The robot will then wait till the C=
ontract completes workflow and becomes 'executed in-effect' before moving o=
n.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f1a335f13a31" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"515e4819a3f4"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"fc041779fbf5">
<td data-local-id=3D"d97178a33ab8" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b5a1499bf088">734</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5acf10e29570" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"aa30110a828d">OrchestrationExportRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c61c9a8c1742" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9ae985f20f4f">Used to export the intake request data to a cl=
ient's external system.&nbsp; Export uses FormRequest.dtd.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8b212f1bb7f8" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7d55f05e2ad7">wfDocExportDestination - connection name</p></=
td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"403e701a2d94"></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"full-width" data-local-id=
=3D"0d48f2e9-faf3-490a-ae06-494844efb7be" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 173.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 385.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 740.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 521.62px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2bc001939e7b">
<td data-local-id=3D"2f0772ec69d4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"aeedc28cbb8f" id=3D"WorkflowRobots-ReceiptRobots"><strong>R=
eceipt Robots</strong></h4></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b31b0d611fb3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3a125678078e"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"07e6beb1fe07" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"23f6571c45c1"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"15cabd4f8d76" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e96b177f75d4"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f87636f8d9ee">
<td data-local-id=3D"c49117d81286" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"105f6b3972ad">710</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2f30f9d7cb42" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a0766bcfe599">OrgReceiptExportSendRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"19428133a998" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"852e8212bee2">Performs a real-time synchronous export of the=
 receipt to the external system. External system is based on the connection=
 assigned to the activity.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ecce4f1dfade" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"64216d2b951c">wfDocExportDestination - connection name <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryCount (0) <br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (300)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4fa9f8eeae94">
<td data-local-id=3D"cd4d8e754604" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1293e06fbda2">715</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"96d429667651" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1130d75c090a">OrgReceiptExportQueueEntryRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0845810bd798" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b22a6727a97c">Inserts the receipt into the export queue.</p>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b8ec9924ba26" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a15fbd137dd3">wfDocExportSchedule - schedule name (Connectio=
n Internal Name)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e48268935dfe">
<td data-local-id=3D"c40efa041d51" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"de0ba6796d55"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5be6c0e01fea" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"78f6e629c3e6">CreateInventoryRobot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1415ba29bb3c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5c7156f7924e">Organizations with Inventory Manager that are =
also implementing receipt workflow are required to add an activity using th=
e create inventory robot in order to generate inventory receipts at the end=
 of receipt workflow. This robot creates inventory receipts for any quantit=
y receipt lines that have the "Add to Inventory" field set to true.</p></td=
>
<td data-local-id=3D"799a61d44c38" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8241732cffee">&lt;Folder folderType=3D"automated" name=3D"Cr=
eate Inventory"&gt;</p>
<p local-id=3D"e1a5b165e92b">&lt;WorkflowType&gt;receipt&lt;/WorkflowType&g=
t;</p>
<p local-id=3D"9c1cc791ab36">&lt;FolderRobot&gt;CreateInventoryRobot&lt;/Fo=
lderRobot&gt;</p>
<p local-id=3D"d2c520dd8fdc">&lt;/Folder&gt;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8a65d77e21c4">
<td data-local-id=3D"b476eeb4e0e1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"645e47120947">719</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8e6f0760372a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d04d0059acca">ReceiptValidationRobotAsynchronous</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ec25e4d1430b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"471d9a0b2442">Creates Receipt Validation Request message and=
 delivers to external system, waits for a response and edits the receipt ac=
cording to values received</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0f06cb0612f5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9cd6453da956">wfDocExportDestination<br>
wfRobotErrorRetryCount (5)<br>
wfRobotErrorRetryInterval (240)<br>
wfRobotSocketReadTimeout (30)</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"43a0fa07c235"></p>
<p local-id=3D"041044b109e3"></p>
    </div>
</body>
